{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Geolocation","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation\"><code>Geolocation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/clearWatch\"><code>clearWatch()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/getCurrentPosition\"><code>getCurrentPosition()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/watchPosition\"><code>watchPosition()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>Geolocation</code></strong> 接口是一个用来获取设备地理位置的可编程的对象，它可以让 Web 内容访问到设备的地理位置，这将允许 Web 应用基于用户的地理位置提供定制的信息。说实话：其实**<code>Geolocation</code>** 就是用来获取到当前设备的经纬度（位置）</p>\n<p>带有此接口的对象可以用由 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a>实现的属性<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/geolocation\"><code>NavigatorGeolocation.geolocation</code></a> 来获得。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 出于安全考虑，当一个 Web 页尝试获取地理位置信息时，会请求用户批准地理位置访问权限。要知道每个浏览器都有自己请求用户批准该权限的策略和方法。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><code>Geolocation</code> 接口不实现，也不继承任何属性。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>Geolocation</code></strong> 接口不继承任何方法。</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"geolocation.getcurrentposition\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/getCurrentPosition\"><code>Geolocation.getCurrentPosition()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>确定设备的位置并返回一个携带位置信息的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/GeolocationPosition\"><code>Position</code></a> 对象。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"geolocation.watchposition\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/watchPosition\"><code>Geolocation.watchPosition()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>注册一个位置改变监听器，每当设备位置改变时，返回一个 <code>long</code> 类型的该监听器的 ID 值。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"geolocation.clearwatch\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/clearWatch\"><code>Geolocation.clearWatch()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>取消由 <code>watchPosition()</code> 注册的位置监听器。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/geolocation-api/#geolocation_interface","title":"Geolocation API"}],"query":"api.Geolocation"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Geolocation","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Geolocation_API\">使用地理位置定位</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"Geolocation 接口是一个用来获取设备地理位置的可编程的对象，它可以让 Web 内容访问到设备的地理位置，这将允许 Web 应用基于用户的地理位置提供定制的信息。说实话：其实**Geolocation** 就是用来获取到当前设备的经纬度（位置）","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Geolocalización","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Geolocation","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/geolocation","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/geolocation/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"i